{"tid":1747192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安局局長李家超選舉前接受中國央視訪問，稱「習近平總書記」要求止暴制亂","createTime":"2019-11-23T06:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T11:30:36.000Z","uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"07e65a061b4c8aea44d079c91259dfd304b26926","tid":1747192,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>稱習近平為總書記　重申止暴制亂目標一致​</strong><br />\n<br />\n整個專訪報道長約5分鐘，分別在央視新聞頻道（CCTV13）和中文國際頻道（CCTV4）播出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3597855/org/c5126eb53472433b70dec5ca9d9f7297.png/XyVYAU2TJjhAEUslryAGnW6YNmaG45x_Znfac2Z32nM?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3597855%2Forg%2Fc5126eb53472433b70dec5ca9d9f7297.png%2FXyVYAU2TJjhAEUslryAGnW6YNmaG45x_Znfac2Z32nM%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=be634599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<del>中共地下黨員</del>李家超最開首兩次引述習近平的說法，但就用上習近平的黨內頭銜「<span style=\"color: red;\">中共中央總書記</span>」來稱呼，指「<span style=\"color: red;\">總書記已經說得很清楚</span>，現在香港最緊迫的任務就是止暴制亂，恢復香港的秩序，這個跟我們的目標是一致的」，以及「而且<span style=\"color: red;\">總書記講的有關三個堅定支持</span>，支持行政長官、支持警隊、支持我們司法機關。」他指，依法嚴懲這些暴行，也是香港目的，「我們當然會以這個方向去落實。」<br />\n<br />\n稱法院盡快有指導性判決很關鍵<br />\n李家超提到兩個方向，分別是「嚴正執法」及「社會共識」，他指至今已拘捕了超過4,000人，「有些時候有些行為，真的是危害人身安全，可以涉及意圖謀殺的一些行為，是非常嚴重的。」李家超認為，除了警方執法和社會譴責暴力外，「法院盡快有一些指導性、權威性的一些判決，讓社會、老百姓、群眾明白什麼是對，什麼是不容許的，這些很關鍵。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>派警把守投票站兼作周邊巡邏</strong><br />\n<br />\n李家超向央視表示，整個特區政府全力投入去確保我們區議員選舉會安全、公平、公正地舉辦，「當然警方是最前線，我知道他們已經有不同的部署，包括針對投票站的安保工作，每一個投票站都有警方的人員把守，第二個呢就是在周邊的環境，要讓老百姓安心去投票，所以他們有一些高姿態的巡邏，針對高風險的地方，當然這方面更會加強，而且警方會有一些快速應變隊伍，如果有什麼情報或者聽到有什麼風吹草動的事情，已經啟動這個快速應變部隊去立即處理。」"},{"pid":"fb1b1bc78bcb401ab55333b8b92427fb46c40b15","tid":1747192,"uid":59461,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"李家超:我們司法機關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d37e93e4f3f08daa21d4e609e9228cca3c2cb1","tid":1747192,"uid":31151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"共產黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49e952fd8137cf63bb2d691c7b9295457169bfe","tid":1747192,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"做乜害習總"},{"pid":"d4fd59960a301abbe12a9e87e670874f50f80f82","tid":1747192,"uid":37869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:20:17.000Z","msg":"歸邊了？<br />\n美國話唔應該叫國家主席 應該叫總書記<br />\n以後要叫雜種書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nUSCC報告︰美國不應稱習近平「國家主席」 避免令人以為中國有民<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191116/60273263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191116%2F60273263&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=67098ce6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191116%2F60273263&h=e6b63234\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191116/60273263</a>"},{"pid":"fe177ba03ef4ba9202e67662f121dbaa0da80a5d","tid":1747192,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>節目中提到新上任的警務處處長<span style=\"color: red;\">鄧炳強</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3597834/org/7fd8aae36335f0c24580ff38dff39dba.png/_2DFQRE-APeKTRUqo-sO89yxOJ2CB9M6Pt806j7fNOo?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3597834%2Forg%2F7fd8aae36335f0c24580ff38dff39dba.png%2F_2DFQRE-APeKTRUqo-sO89yxOJ2CB9M6Pt806j7fNOo%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=d525674f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3598065/org/0e250b49ae64a5d085972b9c3e6e07c0.jpg/xripXtz5cBQNJMBQwctwpPkZDZWCuwRsbxC8BkUQvAY?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3598065%2Forg%2F0e250b49ae64a5d085972b9c3e6e07c0.jpg%2FxripXtz5cBQNJMBQwctwpPkZDZWCuwRsbxC8BkUQvAY%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=1e11a0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<del>中共地下黨員</del>李家超表示，「我覺得警察真的很艱苦，他們很堅定，我也非常感謝，也非常驕傲，我們香港有這麼有效率專業的團隊，無畏無懼去保衛我們香港這個家園。」"},{"pid":"9060aae2bbdc02ba7ad47c1f4b99d75546b8f042","tid":1747192,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2549502/org/1ea30c10457cf75d462586014719b3c4.jpg/PpKZ4pvRWGY1yihP7t2vjX-O63r7K7IGD64K3A-uCtw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2549502%2Forg%2F1ea30c10457cf75d462586014719b3c4.jpg%2FPpKZ4pvRWGY1yihP7t2vjX-O63r7K7IGD64K3A-uCtw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b08fd04e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2936214/org/5e64e9667f57755612021eecaeb16904.jpg/E5gtU1sePXuBt1rJttu3OsJdHhsd4XcGlAg6u5QIOrs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2936214%2Forg%2F5e64e9667f57755612021eecaeb16904.jpg%2FE5gtU1sePXuBt1rJttu3OsJdHhsd4XcGlAg6u5QIOrs&h=a1cc910a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3367c2bed0df135d6d14ec428f8c4f0aae748dca","tid":1747192,"uid":130797,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"「法院盡快有一些指導性、權威性的一些判決，讓社會、老百姓、群眾明白什麼是對，什麼是不容許的，這些很關鍵。」<br />\n<br />\n笑左<br />\n咁建議命令法庭容許違憲既蒙面法繼續執行呢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a33be4e1a88e041513b41a19053371a1da6b02","tid":1747192,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3367c2bed0df135d6d14ec428f8c4f0aae748dca","tid":1747192,"uid":130797,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"「法院盡快有一些指導性、權威性的一些判決，讓社會、老百姓、群眾明白什麼是對，什麼是不容許的，這些很關鍵。」<br />\n<br />\n笑